---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const basePath = baseUrl.endsWith('/') ? baseUrl : `${baseUrl}/`;
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Robert Otieno" description="About Robert Otieno, Enterprise Identity, Security & IT Operations Architect.">
	<section class="hero" style="margin-top: 0;">
		<div>
		<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
		<h1>Architecting Trust Infrastructure for Enterprise Systems</h1>
		<p class="lead">
			I work at the intersection of identity architecture, operational security, and privacy engineering to design resilient enterprise systems.
		</p>
		<p>
			My approach treats identity as infrastructure: access decisions must be measurable, governance must be operationally integrated, and privacy
			must be embedded into the architecture from the start.
		</p>
		<div class="cta-row">
			<a class="cta" href={`${basePath}projects/`}>View Projects</a>
			<a class="cta" href={`${basePath}portfolio/`}>View Portfolio</a>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="hero-art" aria-hidden="true">
			<svg viewBox="0 0 420 280" width="100%">
				<circle cx="90" cy="88" r="38" fill="#f8faff" stroke="#1e3a8a" />
				<circle cx="210" cy="88" r="38" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#94a3b8" />
				<circle cx="330" cy="88" r="38" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#94a3b8" />
				<rect x="50" y="170" width="320" height="66" rx="9" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#cbd5e1" />
				<path d="M128 88 H172" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2" />
				<path d="M248 88 H292" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2" />
				<text x="61" y="208" fill="#1f2937" font-size="13">Identity · Operations · Privacy · Automation</text>
			</svg>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Principles</h2>
		<div class="grid">
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Identity as Control Plane</h3>
				<p>Security posture starts with reliable identity context and consistent access decisions.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Operational Integration</h3>
				<p>Policy value is realized only when IAM controls are embedded in incident and change workflows.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Privacy by Architecture</h3>
				<p>Privacy is treated as a design constraint, not an afterthought, with explicit minimization choices.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Automation for Scale</h3>
				<p>Governance must be repeatable, auditable, and operationally sustainable across enterprise growth.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2>Current Direction</h2>
		<p>
			I am focused on enterprise IAM modernization, access governance transformation, and practical pathways for decentralized identity in
			real-world organizations.
		</p>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>